# BhanksStaking Guide

## Overview
Stake your BHNK tokens to earn passive rewards.
The contract pays 1% per day on staked amount.

## How to stake
1. Connect your wallet on the Stake page
2. Enter the amount of BHNK you want to stake
3. Click Approve — allows the contract to move
   your tokens (first transaction)
4. Click Stake — locks your tokens
   (second transaction)
5. Rewards start accumulating immediately

## How to unstake
1. Go to the Stake page
2. Click Unstake + Claim Rewards
3. Confirm the transaction
4. You receive your stake plus all rewards

## Reward calculation
Rewards = (staked amount x time staked x 1%)
          divided by (100 x 1 day in seconds)

## Risks
- Smart contracts can have bugs
- Contracts are not audited
- Only stake what you can afford to lose
- Test on Base Sepolia before mainnet